652
00:49:33,730 --> 00:49:37,220
Takže, teraz ste sa zvedavý.

653
00:49:39,130 --> 00:49:43,340
Takže, čo si mám vypočuť...

654
00:49:43,340 --> 00:49:45,930
Nesedeli by sme tu takto,

655
00:49:45,930 --> 00:49:49,560
