743
00:56:11,010 --> 00:56:13,820
Pane...

744
00:56:13,820 --> 00:56:18,040
Nebudete schopný to uniesť.

745
00:56:23,740 --> 00:56:25,750
<i>Potom,</i>

746
00:56:25,750 --> 00:56:27,890
<i>dôvod prečo som prišiel na tento svet...</i>

747
00:56:33,040 --> 00:56:36,280
<i>Prestaňte!!!  PRESTAŇTE!!!</i>

748
00:56:36,280 --> 00:56:38,310
<i>PRESTAŇTE S TÝM!!!!</i>

749
00:56:47,800 --> 00:56:51,260
