Ja vytiahnem tiež.

785
00:58:51,230 --> 00:58:53,910
Čo keď odhodím kartu?

786
00:58:55,960 --> 00:58:58,260
Stále...

787
00:58:58,260 --> 00:59:00,750
vám ukážem svoje.

788
00:59:01,140 --> 00:59:03,000
Takže,

789
00:59:03,000 --> 00:59:05,330
ma chcete chytiť?

790
00:59:05,330 --> 00:59:07,530
To je pravda.

791
00:59:07,530 --> 00:59:09,180
Prečo,

792
00:59:09,180 --> 00:59:12,800
by sme si mali ubližovať?

793
00:59:13,790 --> 00:59:16,890
Koniec koncov, chcete

794
00:59:16,890 --> 00:59:19,360
